name: Is Time a Friend ?
description:
Is time a friend in this world? Does time benefit your life or does it mess up your life?
imagine if the sun does not shine on the earth, will time still help us in life? what if the clock never existed or the scientist who determined the 24 hours of the day didn't exist, what would happen? 

Maybe our life is the same as a temple that is still standing but useless.....
We become fragile and became targets of predators out there.....

This is life, too many unanswered questions....

Like a friend who helps us but also stands in our shadows...
